---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ABOH LEGAL"
  description="Privacy Policy for the ABOH LEGAL website. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <Hero label="Legal" title="Privacy Policy" />

  <section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-10">

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">ABOH LEGAL ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting the privacy of visitors to our website (www.abohlegal.ca). This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information in compliance with the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA).</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">We collect personal information only when you voluntarily provide it through our contact form: your name, email address, phone number, and message content. We also collect optional information about how you heard about us.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">We use the information you provide solely to respond to your inquiry, evaluate whether we can assist with your legal matter, and communicate with you about our services. We do not use your information for marketing purposes without your consent.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-4">Our website uses the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-text leading-relaxed">
          <li><strong>Formspree</strong> — Processes contact form submissions. See Formspree's privacy policy at <a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Maps</strong> — Provides the embedded map on our Contact page. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">Google's privacy policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — Hosts our website. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gold hover:underline">Vercel's privacy policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mt-4">Our analytics solution (when implemented) will be privacy-friendly and will not use cookies or track personally identifiable information.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">This website does not use cookies for tracking or analytics purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">We retain contact form submissions only as long as necessary to respond to your inquiry and for our legitimate business purposes. If a solicitor-client relationship is not established, your inquiry information is retained in accordance with the Law Society of Alberta's record-keeping requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">7. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-4">Under PIPEDA, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-body-text leading-relaxed">
          <li>Access your personal information held by us</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for the use of your information</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mt-4">To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@abohlegal.ca" class="text-gold hover:underline">info@abohlegal.ca</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">Our website is not directed at children under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-navy text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3">11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed">Privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:info@abohlegal.ca" class="text-gold hover:underline">info@abohlegal.ca</a> or <a href="tel:+18254610107" class="text-gold hover:underline">(825) 461-0107</a>.</p>
        <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mt-2">ABOH LEGAL, 4437 53 Avenue, St. Paul, AB T0A 3A2.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
